===[[Season 1]]===
She stumbles into a meeting between [[Petyr Baelish|Littlefinger]] and [[Catelyn Stark]] and is waved away.<ref>"[[Lord Snow]]"</ref> Later on she attracts the attention of [[Jory Cassel]] during Lord [[Eddard Stark]]'s visit to the brothel.<ref>"[[The Wolf and the Lion]]"</ref>
